[ORCHESTRA PLAYING BRASSY,
PATRIOTIC MUSIC]

1452
01:20:26,238 --> 01:20:29,699
[SINGING] There's a feeling comes a-stealing
And it sets my brain a-reeling

1453
01:20:29,909 --> 01:20:33,411
When I listen to the music
Of a military band

1454
01:20:33,621 --> 01:20:37,081
Every tune like "Yankee Doodle"
Simply sets me off my noodle

1455
01:20:37,291 --> 01:20:41,252
It's that patriotic something
That no one can understand

1456
01:20:41,462 --> 01:20:43,213
CHORUS:
Way down south in the land of cotton

1457
01:20:43,422 --> 01:20:45,924
Melody untiring

1458
01:20:46,133 --> 01:20:48,176
It's so inspiring

1459
