CHORUS: Hurrah, hurrah
We joined the jubilee

1460
01:20:52,139 --> 01:20:55,725
And that's going some
For the Yankees, by gum

1461
01:20:55,935 --> 01:20:59,354
Red, white and blue
I am for you

1462
