And forever in peace may you wave

1465
01:21:10,199 --> 01:21:12,283
You're the emblem of

1466
01:21:12,493 --> 01:21:14,077
The land I love

1467
01:21:14,286 --> 01:21:17,288
ALL:
The home of the free and the brave

1468
01:21:17,498 --> 01:21:21,084
Every heart beats true
Under red, white and blue

1469
01:21:21,293 --> 01:21:24,629
Where there's never a boast or brag

1470
01:21:24,839 --> 01:21:28,383
ALL:
But should old acquaintance be forgot

1471
01:21:28,592 --> 01:21:31,261
Keep your eye on that grand old flag

1472
01:21:31,470 --> 01:21:35,640
CHORUS: Rally round the flag
Let us rally round the flag

1473
01:21:37,518 --> 01:21:40,603
We took the red
from the flame of dawn...

1474
01:21:40,813 --> 01:21:42,522
...the dawn of a new nation.

1475
01:21:42,731 --> 01:21:46,776
And the white was the white
of the snow at Valley Forge.

1476
01:21:46,986 --> 01:21:50,947
The blue was the blue
of the free, open sky...

1477
01:21:51,156 --> 01:21:54,909
...and the stars were
the 13 sisters by the sea...

1478
01:21:55,119 --> 01:21:58,830
...who built their home
and called it liberty.

1479
